original: Holmdahl, Jonas Viktor, läroverksadjunkt, Borås, f. 5/3/83 i Tvååker, Hall. 1., av kontr :prosten Svante Julius Edvard H. o. Anna Elisabet Lars-son-Laurell. G. 16 m. Annie Elam. Barn: Anna f. 17, g. m. med. lic. Erik
translated: Holmdahl, Jonas Viktor, high school teacher, Borås, born on March 5, 1883 in Tvååker, Halland county, the first child of district parish priest Svante Julius Edvard H. and Anna Elisabet Lars-son-Laurell. Married on 1916 with Annie Elam. They had a daughter named Anna, born in 1917, who married medical doctor Erik.
